h2 Viewing people

table.table
  thead
    tr
      th[scope="col"] ID
      th[scope="col"] Name
      th[scope="col"] Phone number
      th[scope="col"] Email address
      th[scope="col"] Company
  tbody
    - @people.each do |person|
      tr
        th[scope="row"]= person&.id
        td= person.try(:name)
        td= person.try(:phone_number)
        td= person.try(:email)
        td= person.try(:company).try(:name)

= paginate @people, theme: 'bootstrap3'
= page_entries_info @people


